---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout title="Transcen.Digital">
  <div class="transcen-main-content">
    <section class="hero-section">
      <div class="hero-overlay"></div>

      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1 class="hero-title">
          Navigate the Future
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">
          Design systems that deliver clarity, flow, and digital advantage
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="prose lg:prose-lg max-w-4xl mx-auto my-12 px-4">
      <p>
        I help organizations unlock meaningful change through clarity, experimentation, and better ways of working. Digital transformation isn't just about technology—it's about designing systems that improve <strong>flow</strong>, deliver <strong>value</strong>, and make room for <strong>joy</strong> in the work itself.
      </p>

      <p>
        Whether you're wrestling with outdated delivery models, planning for AI, or rethinking your org design, I partner with teams to turn aspiration into execution—without defaulting to buzzwords, off-the-shelf frameworks, or one-size-fits-all solutions.
      </p>

      <p>Here's how I help:</p>

      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Emerging Tech & AI Integration</strong> – Cut through the noise. Build an AI strategy grounded in real value and real people.</li>
        <li><strong>Strategic Planning & Execution</strong> – Translate bold ideas into executable plans—and build the system needed to make them real.</li>
        <li><strong>Digital Solution Delivery</strong> – From prototype to production, I help teams build better digital products and services.</li>
        <li><strong>Enterprise Agile Transformation</strong> – Bring agility to life at every level—from the portfolio to the squad—without losing your soul.</li>
        <li><strong>Change & Transition Management</strong> – Create change strategies that actually stick, rooted in purpose and aligned to your culture.</li>
        <li><strong>Product & Portfolio Management</strong> – Align your roadmap to reality. Deliver what matters, faster—and more consistently.</li>
        <li><strong>Stakeholder Alignment & Facilitation</strong> – Get everyone on the same page, fast. From strategy to sticky notes, I help leaders align and act.</li>
        <li><strong>Enterprise Agile SDLC & Compliance</strong> – Balance speed and structure. Build workflows that meet audit needs without killing momentum.</li>
        <li><strong>Operational Efficiency & Cost Reduction</strong> – Identify bottlenecks. Improve end-to-end flow. Drive measurable, sustainable improvement.</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        Ready to rethink how your organization works? Let's talk about how we can make change real—and lasting.
      </p>

      <h2>Let's Connect</h2>
      <p>
        Want to talk transformation, talent, or anything else? Reach out to me on
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ben-van-glabbeek" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
